  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fff39a9b-a7e6-43e9-883e-27ce74eaa9c9\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b21663bd-4dd2-4d0b-849f-de17dd53e1f9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8c842525-a551-463c-a2e7-c4bae281c0a5\"><b>안녕하세요 남성역 한의원, 이수한의원 입니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-fff39a9b-a7e6-43e9-883e-27ce74eaa9c9\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-81ae4a55-503e-4f0f-9c46-e6b0062eabb8\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n                                <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" data-linkdata='{\"src\" : \"\", \"packCode\" : \"motion2d_01\", \"seq\" : \"10\", \"width\" : \"\", \"height\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/motion2d_01/original_10.png?type=p100_100\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" />\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-93bdc531-8d63-4dbf-b590-26e6804f9d10\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-60410b84-6e94-4da7-a14b-59e2b1e7af02\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ed7b9c5d-9cf2-49d1-a2fa-a886efe9889a\"><b>행복한 출산 뒤, 방심은 금물! 산후풍 예방과 관리</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fe449c5a-c217-45bb-9e2c-9544c59d88c0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-26cac1da-0857-471a-8cad-be89e13986db\">아이를 품에 안은 기쁨도 잠시, 출산 직후 여성의 몸은 큰 변화를 겪습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4210baa3-1767-4c3f-9a38-10ee9453aa73\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-67ba3d98-50b7-4db9-ab19-e7e1e2df9331\">이 시기에 제대로 관리하지 않으면 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2caee69e-040b-4641-922d-c4cb812e2c53\"><b>산후풍</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-7e598f8e-6761-45f0-b694-e4bfc1f9411d\">이 찾아와 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cfa22501-ab89-432e-90b0-0fedfa9da101\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-5079e840-75ae-48a0-958d-9ed946277e05\">오랜 시간 불편을 겪을 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-efa5102a-c016-4f18-95b8-152c5d6518d5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-5c20d0d4-bcf3-4303-aa5b-287245a2199c\">산후풍은 단순한 통증이 아니라, </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5d5ff464-c718-4f68-8085-18fe85512415\"><b>평생 건강을 좌우할 수 있는 문제</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-7930a0c5-b93b-4e78-b54a-00f662cf08c3\">이기에 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fc94f191-264c-460b-b9d3-41499c308d9c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-cbffd03a-545c-4ce3-8896-b02a356ef907\">출산 직후의 관리가 무엇보다 중요합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-93bdc531-8d63-4dbf-b590-26e6804f9d10\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-e869b24d-8093-47cc-b617-c814a38de84c\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-613c7b49-b1d0-4412-be0d-94be77e768fc\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-613c7b49-b1d0-4412-be0d-94be77e768fc\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a4592b3b14626f91.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1600\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1600\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\" }'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a4592b3b14626f91.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a4592b3b14626f91.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-613c7b49-b1d0-4412-be0d-94be77e768fc\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-5632d346-6aed-4ae2-9b4d-12954a197a88\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1a31b78e-2156-4d78-b583-8596c23c2189\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7a35b6e6-4689-48a5-8cdc-edab7c71d758\"><b>산후풍의 주요 증상과 원인</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-589f25bf-3b68-4835-ace2-cf1b2b4ad284\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-62dba618-c909-4a53-a1fd-e3d581dd3a76\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-58c39aee-5b49-427e-a0ea-19c9e70ec78c\">산후풍은 출산 후 기혈이 약해지고, 외부의 찬 기운이나 잘못된 생활습관이 겹치면서 발생합니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-78512d80-be62-457f-8928-d883cec15237\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-3859fd63-fcde-4235-8666-72ad3cd6e6c8\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-98dd107c-58d9-4f19-86fe-460fbcdb7853\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-ebe5ff7a-5301-4f38-8f69-b02ef2356d4d\">대표적인 원인</span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a3417eb6-0cdc-41fe-94e2-07d44d57e9a0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c260b1d5-a640-40a1-82a1-7d506eb17d89\"><b>혈허</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-70990bce-3bc8-4227-87c2-77137bcef585\">: 출산 과정에서 혈이 크게 손상되어 나타나는 기력 저하, 어지럼증, 관절통</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f80e73ed-e738-4910-b392-01813f894c55\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7a2d9941-de3e-4658-8ced-7bda99c2351a\"><b>외감</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-4674452b-f762-410e-ade6-574b03056cd5\">: 찬바람·습기 등 외부 자극이 허약한 몸에 침투</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-aeb0357b-d1b8-41d4-af17-30cdf21331e2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5a805e97-3b06-47a2-aeaa-0597b5029bac\"><b>어혈</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-2a3eae3c-1827-4a16-ab2d-9a82e9f58b6b\">: 출산 후 남은 어혈이 몸속에서 순환을 막아 통증 유발</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2c3cc08b-6f3f-4b87-9ece-47a4664c9fc4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bc547784-3bd9-4d19-909e-1f7278186b8e\"><b>신허</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-3aae1181-bd07-4719-ab64-1044c1a7ceed\">: 출산으로 신장의 기운이 약해져 허리통증, 피로, 우울감 동반</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b1538595-c988-4822-9e9e-13fbe83d6d82\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-a8ad3865-0b0b-4792-844c-190eaeeb4f39\">증상으로는 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-efcedc21-0f38-412e-a0af-efd02807fd2c\"><b>관절이 시리고 저린 느낌, 만성 피로, 두통, 우울감</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-6293292f-9455-41fb-8f7e-441983938ccc\"> 등이 흔히 </span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-82bba240-6dbb-4205-b69e-7fcb855501dd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-aba99434-dc28-4cf8-ab5e-ec20b35af9ad\">나타납니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-589f25bf-3b68-4835-ace2-cf1b2b4ad284\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-8dd11100-4384-4820-8a19-fe2c95299c66\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-d71d4526-e5a6-4644-a148-75ec1375a882\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-09887231-8795-474f-82c9-af1104c1bfbc\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8a8ad331-c0ad-44c2-ae04-9209912d443f\"><b>출산 후 골든타임(6~8주) 관리법</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-642ed12b-1a1e-4b43-8104-f866f022d5f4\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-859e4772-08a8-45e1-85de-9c7c62ff56b3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-52baa317-7334-4216-b1df-ea6c3c39cf10\">출산 후 6~8주는 몸을 회복시키는 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ecc76ddd-f307-48aa-a6f0-509c495b9942\"><b>골든타임</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-69d13e92-586f-433e-9af0-e9d2bf6d91d7\">입니다.</span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-117e5155-16fa-4999-a08f-a59615aedd2d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-cab7e979-e29f-435a-b3bf-418ccc02ec43\">충분한 휴식과 보온 유지</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-98c717b3-8265-4d1a-b679-7df0eaf433cb\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-40666b6a-69b7-45be-9ebc-86a9ed074f1a\">찬 음식, 찬물 사용 피하기</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c4092c06-ba33-4355-8716-53d41df4a5ef\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-183c7245-d2b1-40e8-bf88-d6a9987ed288\">규칙적인 수유·수면 리듬 유지</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ca2a63d9-c775-447f-9a00-a5b1117e985f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-b679b5b0-c28a-47ae-b8a9-ce7830bb5626\">맞춤 한약 복용으로 기혈 보충</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c9476c7e-2345-468c-90b2-5b8c4f2781b3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-710c2ab3-fa63-496a-b9d5-a54f03d765fb\">이 시기를 잘 관리하면 산후풍을 예방하고 빠른 회복을 기대할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-642ed12b-1a1e-4b43-8104-f866f022d5f4\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-129203d7-dbbb-4392-9030-77c8d06d4d87\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-d35b1163-a998-49bb-9b9a-32195ca0ba4e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d36cb8d5-efc3-48b9-aee2-31a805b2771c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ccc31b45-84c1-4285-b51b-b5752e64f207\"><b>산후풍을 악화시키는 잘못된 생활습관</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c56f461d-673c-4b7c-b713-017ad5816192\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1d8baa86-5ae5-41df-a0c6-f70204e97923\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-02bff21c-117e-4fb1-9fbb-82282a4c151e\">출산 직후 무리한 가사·육아 노동</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-38007534-3abd-4cbd-bdaa-b69b4979c396\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-d3d8087f-a7f9-43de-93c8-2270e0804b77\">찬 음식, 얼음 음료 섭취</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0c70c6d3-3bd8-4e28-9191-36b69f721f37\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-af43e13f-d9ec-4c09-9619-0afd9561db9a\">허리를 굽히거나 무거운 짐 들기</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8733f206-c059-4a8c-a934-08fe432cd075\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-b72ddcf8-940a-458e-bf3a-c264e9827393\">난방 부족으로 몸을 차게 두는 습관</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1e3de574-2bff-4d72-b499-e8089d47a8da\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-e4f2000a-1654-475d-a6fb-4367d9a97042\">이러한 생활은 기혈 회복을 방해하고 통증을 심화시킬 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-c56f461d-673c-4b7c-b713-017ad5816192\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-8f76ab26-3dba-4468-ae37-f2be4435a7c2\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-918ce02e-4cc4-4199-9c7a-e458bafc1f00\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-135b9c78-e856-43eb-a24c-60981d49f2b7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-16b6bd6d-1ed2-44b2-a86b-d19a2fbab718\"><b>예방과 회복을 돕는 관리법</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a69bcf0f-c848-4e77-9f5f-6520f020a3a4\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8770d4ce-477f-4ca1-9575-da90a338cda9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c3867f76-0540-4127-809e-9e2876b72e20\"><b>한약 치료</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-fc3f5a0b-aa1a-4bf3-a483-10631292c140\">: 기혈 보충, 어혈 제거, 체질 맞춤 회복 도움</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0bc56ddf-8455-427e-8d7d-f6cc41b3d1c4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7ec34462-d70e-4497-b644-c2a94e5c797c\"><b>침·뜸 치료</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-dbd8e7e0-84fd-4602-b6f1-9069d734a19a\">: 관절 통증 완화, 기혈 순환 촉진</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-42d4cb3d-4a97-4e61-a9dd-956d78eb00c4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-62a3618e-287b-4d9b-9f30-2497270a7600\"><b>운동</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-11a533e3-9d32-43b0-843f-51284730d309\">: 산후 요가, 가벼운 스트레칭으로 근육·관절 회복</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b88d3188-674d-4c96-8aa9-6929fec85cc1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0e2aa618-f39c-4be6-9c2c-180d73fd6e04\"><b>식습관 관리</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-b4fa0b80-b0aa-4ddd-8ad3-510e2ea39bdb\">: 따뜻하고 소화 잘 되는 음식, 단백질·철분 보충</span></p></li></ul><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-a69bcf0f-c848-4e77-9f5f-6520f020a3a4\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-82ca001c-26d1-4fd5-b80e-f1a035b9bdb3\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-82ca001c-26d1-4fd5-b80e-f1a035b9bdb3\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/15963058e7cdfb11.png\", \"o